{"tid":1949295,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"ities:Skylines 自由度最大建城遊戲(10) Sunset Harbor 1.13.0-f7","createTime":"2020-03-29T14:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T14:06:37.000Z","uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ecae924f6e12e6175c1b6129f22ef2b7dc0c367f","tid":1949295,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:04:55.000Z","msg":"Cities:Skylines 自由度最大建城遊戲(10) Sunset Harbor 1.13.0-f7<br />\n<br />\n9. <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1185640/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1185640/page/1</a><br />\n10. (here) <br />\n<br />\n- Steam Store: [url]<a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/255710/[/center][/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F255710%2F%5B%2Fcenter%5D%5B%2Furl%5D&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq9fEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=8d8e33df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://store.steampowered.com/app/255710/[/center][/url]</a><br />\n- Steam Workshop: <a href=\"http://steamcommunity.com/app/255710/workshop/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsteamcommunity.com%2Fapp%2F255710%2Fworkshop%2F&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq9fEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=cf67dc1c\" target=\"_blank\">http://steamcommunity.com/app/255710/workshop/</a><br />\n- Paradox forum: <a href=\"https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/index.php?forums/cities-skylines.859/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.paradoxplaza.com%2Fforum%2Findex.php%3Fforums%2Fcities-skylines.859%2F&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq9fEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=7c76b905\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/index.php?forums/cities-skylines.859/</a><br />\n- Simtropolis: <a href=\"https://community.simtropolis.com/forums/forum/270-cities-skylines/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcommunity.simtropolis.com%2Fforums%2Fforum%2F270-cities-skylines%2F&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq9fEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=fa771018\" target=\"_blank\">https://community.simtropolis.com/forums/forum/270-cities-skylines/</a><br />\n- Reddit: /r/CitiesSkylines, /r/CitiesSkylinesModding, /r/ShittySkylines<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">遊戲特色</span></ins><br />\n- 模擬城市經營類<br />\n- 自訂巴士路線<br />\n- 自己拉水拉電<br />\n- 可以劃分唔同區域,唔同區域可以有唔同既政策(policy)<br />\n- 遊戲鼓勵玩家做MOD, Steam workshop有幾萬個mod, 乜都有, 包括中文版mod<br />\nIGN 8.5/10 佳作<br />\n巴哈姆特 9.1 /10 佳作<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">購買前需知Q&amp;A</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&gt;&gt;遊戲只支援64bits Windows&lt;&lt; 32bits請升級返先好玩</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1) 豪華版同普通版有咩分別??<br />\nA: 豪華版比普通版只係多5座建築物<br />\n<br />\n2) kinguin買key信得過嗎?<br />\nA: 好多巴打都用依個網搵平key, 最重要係你要sure佢係寫住Worldwide (全球key)<br />\n買完係Steam入面直接REDEEM就OK, 唔明可以留言問我地<br />\n<br />\n3) 除左KINGUIN邊度仲可以買到?<br />\nA: GMG都有做緊特價, 但只得8折 <a href=\"http://www.greenmangaming.com/s/hk/en/pc/games/simulation/cities-skylines/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.greenmangaming.com%2Fs%2Fhk%2Fen%2Fpc%2Fgames%2Fsimulation%2Fcities-skylines%2F&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq9fEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=2ff277c5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.greenmangaming.com/s/hk/en/pc/games/simulation/cities-skylines/</a> 普通版,<br />\nGMG夏日20%off(八折) key: GMGSUM-MERSAL-E20OFF (請留意GMG主頁,code會每兩星期變更)<br />\n<br />\n4) 淘寶買有冇事?<br />\nA: 首先，Steam係會鎖區既。淘寶買既Steam Key主要分左 俄區, 國區, 世界Key。俄區/國區key需要比個account賣家去幫你activate，gift方法亦存在好大風險會鎖帳號。當然我唔可以話一定鎖, 但淘寶買既風險自己要諗清楚承擔返。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>基本Q&amp;A</ins><br />\n<br />\nQ:點解成日玩玩下死好多人<br />\nA:因為人係會死,得6年命 你同一區住宅一齊起左左幾萬人 就會幾萬人一齊死 （death wave）<br />\n<br />\nQ:起完水壩氾濫點算好<br />\nA:可以起抽水器抽走<br />\n<br />\n[...] (WIP)<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">MOD篇</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n遊戲公司鼓勵大家安裝/設計mod<br />\n只要係正版, 只需入steam cities skyline既workshop揀岩就按訂閱就會自動下載 安裝埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nCSL Modding Info: <a href=\"https://cslmodding.info/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcslmodding.info%2F&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq9fEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=43892732\" target=\"_blank\">https://cslmodding.info/</a><br />\n<br />\nMod Compatability Checker: <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/workshop/filedetails/?id=2034713132\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamcommunity.com%2Fworkshop%2Ffiledetails%2F%3Fid%3D2034713132&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq9fEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=db02f547\" target=\"_blank\">https://steamcommunity.com/workshop/filedetails/?id=2034713132</a><br />\n<br />\n正體字 mod:<br />\nTraditional Chinese Translation V2 社群正體中文化 V2<br />\n<a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=938512234\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamcommunity.com%2Fsharedfiles%2Ffiledetails%2F%3Fid%3D938512234&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq9fEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=93082793\" target=\"_blank\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=938512234</a><br />\n<br />\n[...] (WIP)<br />\n<br />\nMod Compatibility: （亦即係比較新同update嘅 mod list）:<br />\n<a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/app/255710/discussions/0/1870623125774285868/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamcommunity.com%2Fapp%2F255710%2Fdiscussions%2F0%2F1870623125774285868%2F&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq9fEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=1e081d9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://steamcommunity.com/app/255710/discussions/0/1870623125774285868/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1mVFkj_7ij4FLzKs2QJaONNmb9Z-SRqUeG6xFGqEX1ew/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1mVFkj_7ij4FLzKs2QJaONNmb9Z-SRqUeG6xFGqEX1ew%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq9fEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=00935324\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1mVFkj_7ij4FLzKs2QJaONNmb9Z-SRqUeG6xFGqEX1ew/edit?usp=sharing<